| **Consumption** | Pests eat crops | Releases energy |
| **Predation** | Small â†” Large | TRANSFER of energy between bodies |
| **Decay** | Corpses, waste, residue | SINKS into soil |
| **Heat** | Decomposition | BUILDS under surface |
| **Friction** | All interactions | STRESS on the system |

